data.description: October completion date! Lennar's newly designed two-level townhome set in desirable Lakewood. You will appreciate the low-maintenance lifestyle with front landscaping and snow removal included. 9' ceilings and 8' doors on the main level are standard, along with home automation, energy-efficient technology, whole-home wi-fi, Ring Alarm Security Kit, Ring Video Doorbell Pro, smart lock, thermostat and garage control. This home is that perfect blend of open floorplan along with upgraded features, like granite countertops and vinyl flooring, that everyone is looking for! The open area features Delfino EVP flooring and encompasses the kitchen, breakfast nook and great room. Entertaining is a breeze in the kitchen with Silver Falls granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, fawn subway tile kitchen backsplash and Espresso cabinets. The owner's suite is located for optimal privacy from the secondary bedroom and includes an en-suite bathroom with granite countertops, LVT flooring and a walk-in closet. 2' faux wood blinds are even included in all privacy areas. This is low maintenance living at its best! This amazing community offers a pool and cabana, community playground, and so many trails to enjoy as you step out your front door! Fantastic location just a short distance to the foothills and Red Rocks, as well as Bear Creek Lake Park, Fox Hollow Golf Course, Belmar Shopping District, and less than 20 minutes to Downtown Denver. It's Lennar, so everything's included! The home
